Barnaby Joyce has spoken out after Amber Heard revealed she had named her new puppy after him. 
The American actress, 35, and her Hollywood star ex Johnny Depp, 58, clashed with the politician back in 2015 after illegally transporting their dogs into Australia. 
Amber revealed she hadn't forgotten
